An online music platform, Next Music TV, has been launched recently. For the 24-hour online gospel music, television, which had over 100,000 viewers on its first day of broadcast, it was gathered that the platform was created to propagate and disseminate the gospel of Jesus Christ. Presently, Next Music TV has about a million viewers from across 20 countries and a daily viewership of over 80,000 people live-streaming new releases, trending videos and musical concerts from different artistes. “Once you subscribe, you will get notifications on programmes like ‘The Hits,’ ‘Art of Praise,’ ‘Light up with music,’ ‘Gospel turn up’ and ‘Just Gospel.’ It also gives you first-hand information on new and upcoming gospel music, “ an inside source stated. 